CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13, reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet - Founders - Members of the New York chapter of Girl Friends, who were founders of the club group 30 years ago, include, standing, Connie Cotterell and Anna Murphy; seated, Henri Youngue and Eunice Shreeves, new of Chicago."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four women, standing from left: Connie Cotterell and Anna Murphy; seated: Henri Youngue and Eunice Shreeves, in Penn-Sheraton Hotel for Thirtieth Anniversary Convention of Girl Friends, Inc. brunch
